extend layout

block content
    h1 Welcome
    br
    p.
        Pollstr is an online voting/polling application. Use it to conduct polls
        in either the 
        <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/First-past-the-post_voting">first-past-the-post</a>
        method, the 
        <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Instant-runoff_voting">instant run-off</a>,
        or the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borda_count">Borda count</a> method.
        Visit the <a href="/about">Methods</a> page for a brief overview of the various methods.
    br
    p Please log in or register to create, vote, share, and moderate polls.
    
block scripts
    script(src='/js/index.js')
